               <msContents defective="false">
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1" defective="false">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donors; name of the protagonist (both Libanos and Mäṭaˤ); in Text I, groups of lines on the incipit page of the prologue (fol. 3r) and on the incipit page of the proper account (fol. 17r), and the incipit of some subsections; in Text II, groups of lines on the incipit page, and incipit of each miracle; in Text III, groups of lines on the incipit page and the word sälam (and its abbreviation); elements of the punctuation signs, text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
